    <h3 style="text-align:justify">Join Dive Division Club now &amp; start diving regularly on Curacao!</h3>

<p style="text-align:justify">Do you want to dive regularly but find it hard to get a buddy to come along? Do you like to share your experience after a dive with other divers? Do you want to receive discounts at the dive center and watersports retail store? Then become a member of the Dive Division Club.</p>

<p style="text-align:justify">You are able to dive every 2 weeks at a minimum, with other club members, according to a pre-set year schedule. The exact dive location will be determined by the hosting dive center. There will always be a certified divemaster present during our Dive Division Club dives.</p>

<p style="text-align:justify">Everyone may become a member. To join at a dive you need to have a PADI open water license (or similar).</p>

<p style="text-align:justify">Yearly membership fee:</p>

<ul>
    <li style="text-align:justify">Sedula holder: ANG 25,00 per year.</li>
    <li style="text-align:justify">No Sedula: US$ 25,00 per year.<br/>
       </li>
</ul>

<h3 style="text-align:justify">Benefits</h3>

<p style="text-align:justify">Upon showing your membership card you will obtain a discount   at these dive centers and retail stores:</p>

<ul>
